1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 13]

2
00:00:28,776 --> 00:00:29,255
Do you want to

3
00:00:29,256 --> 00:00:30,615
work for the Marshal?

4
00:00:31,736 --> 00:00:32,575
The pay

5
00:00:32,576 --> 00:00:34,255
is much better than being a policeman.

6
00:00:36,536 --> 00:00:38,055
The little money you earn

7
00:00:38,696 --> 00:00:42,495
probably can't compete with Zhou Yimo.

8
00:00:48,216 --> 00:00:48,775
Miss An,

9
00:00:50,336 --> 00:00:51,175
what exactly are you trying to say?

10
00:00:51,496 --> 00:00:53,455
Though childhood friends may be talented and capable,

11
00:00:54,536 --> 00:00:55,575
you still can't compare to

12
00:00:55,576 --> 00:00:56,895
the young master of a wealthy family.

13
00:01:01,576 --> 00:01:03,975
Whether it's wealth, power, or ambition,

14
00:01:04,736 --> 00:01:05,855
here with the Marshal,

15
00:01:04,910 --> 00:01:08,740
[Lu Huaiji, the marshal]

16
00:01:06,256 --> 00:01:07,295
you can achieve it all.

17
00:01:07,656 --> 00:01:08,455
Thank you, Marshal.

18
00:01:08,816 --> 00:01:11,015
I will go through fire and water for you,

19
00:01:11,016 --> 00:01:12,295
no matter the cost.

20
00:01:12,336 --> 00:01:12,895
Report!

21
00:01:14,856 --> 00:01:15,455
Marshal,

22
00:01:15,696 --> 00:01:16,895
Master Zhou

23
00:01:17,016 --> 00:01:17,815
is here again.

24
00:01:18,616 --> 00:01:19,695
For such a minor matter,

25
00:01:20,216 --> 00:01:21,335
why not let Deputy Yu

26
00:01:21,336 --> 00:01:22,575
handle it for you?

27
00:01:22,736 --> 00:01:23,175
Fine.

28
00:01:23,656 --> 00:01:24,455
Deputy Yu,

29
00:01:24,736 --> 00:01:26,015
if someone asks for my help,

30
00:01:26,216 --> 00:01:27,895
they must pay the price.

31
00:01:28,336 --> 00:01:29,135
Understand?

32
00:01:30,856 --> 00:01:31,615
Deputy Yu,

33
00:01:33,456 --> 00:01:34,855
you'll handle this well, right?

34
00:01:38,536 --> 00:01:39,015
Yes.

35
00:01:40,936 --> 00:01:42,255
[Zhongshan Hospital]

36
00:01:43,936 --> 00:01:44,535
Fifth concubine,

37
00:01:45,056 --> 00:01:45,815
have something to eat.

38
00:01:47,136 --> 00:01:48,855
Has anyone noticed we are missing?

39
00:01:49,056 --> 00:01:50,455
The residence is in chaos right now,

40
00:01:50,696 --> 00:01:51,855
so no one has discovered

41
00:01:51,856 --> 00:01:53,055
your or the young master's whereabouts.

42
00:01:55,096 --> 00:01:56,935
Being unnoticed has its advantages.

43
00:01:58,296 --> 00:01:59,015
Return to the residence first.

44
00:02:00,136 --> 00:02:01,655
We need someone inside to feed us information.

45
00:02:07,896 --> 00:02:09,375
Using your body to block bullets?

46
00:02:11,216 --> 00:02:13,015
Do you think you're indestructible?

47
00:02:14,096 --> 00:02:15,495
Well, aren't I?

48
00:02:18,536 --> 00:02:19,255
You're awake.

49
00:02:20,856 --> 00:02:21,735
I'll call the doctor.

50
00:02:24,936 --> 00:02:25,855
I'm fine.

51
00:02:26,256 --> 00:02:27,295
You're not fine!

52
00:02:27,976 --> 00:02:29,375
Do you realize you almost...

53
00:02:30,176 --> 00:02:31,455
Without your permission,

54
00:02:32,496 --> 00:02:33,535
I wouldn't dare die.

55
00:02:34,016 --> 00:02:35,015
How can you

56
00:02:35,416 --> 00:02:36,455
even joke at a time like this?

57
00:02:36,736 --> 00:02:37,935
I swear I'll tear your mouth apart if you keep it up.

58
00:02:43,496 --> 00:02:45,375
Don't let them in yet.

59
00:02:45,376 --> 00:02:46,495
Don't be so stubborn.

60
00:02:46,896 --> 00:02:48,095
Just two minutes.

61
00:02:49,976 --> 00:02:50,815
Sit down.

62
00:02:51,016 --> 00:02:52,175
Stay with me, okay?

63
00:03:16,496 --> 00:03:17,535
Why are you looking at me like that?

64
00:03:18,496 --> 00:03:20,375
Isn't this much better now?

65
00:03:22,736 --> 00:03:24,215
You're just Ye Zhiqiu,

66
00:03:25,856 --> 00:03:27,215
not the Zhou family's Fifth concubine.

67
00:03:28,976 --> 00:03:30,375
I'm just Zhou Yimo,

68
00:03:31,856 --> 00:03:33,855
not the Zhou family's young master.

69
00:03:36,256 --> 00:03:37,215
We're just

70
00:03:37,776 --> 00:03:39,575
two ordinary equals.

71
00:03:44,856 --> 00:03:45,935
No matter what status

72
00:03:46,976 --> 00:03:47,735
or title,

73
00:03:49,416 --> 00:03:50,815
we are who we truly are.

74
00:03:52,496 --> 00:03:54,375
I'll tell you what

75
00:03:55,576 --> 00:03:56,975
I wanted to say in the car now.

76
00:03:59,856 --> 00:04:02,135
If it's some mushy nonsense,

77
00:04:04,496 --> 00:04:05,535
then don't say it.

78
00:04:11,496 --> 00:04:12,655
When one day

79
00:04:12,856 --> 00:04:14,135
I become the head of the household,

80
00:04:16,376 --> 00:04:18,295
I will grant you your freedom.

81
00:04:22,376 --> 00:04:23,015
Freedom?

82
00:04:24,856 --> 00:04:26,135
Let you be yourself,

83
00:04:28,456 --> 00:04:30,375
not dependent on any faction,

84
00:04:31,136 --> 00:04:32,655
nor anyone's concubine.

85
00:04:33,776 --> 00:04:35,615
Continue studying if you wish,

86
00:04:36,656 --> 00:04:38,495
find work if you want to work.

87
00:04:39,616 --> 00:04:41,095
I'll support you when you're tired,

88
00:04:43,576 --> 00:04:45,495
but you'll have absolute freedom

89
00:04:46,856 --> 00:04:48,855
to control your own life.

90
00:04:55,856 --> 00:04:57,375
Is this what you wanted to tell me?

91
00:04:58,376 --> 00:04:59,855
What else should I say?

92
00:05:01,456 --> 00:05:02,255
So

93
00:05:03,856 --> 00:05:05,255
what were you expecting me to say?

94
00:05:07,896 --> 00:05:09,095
I'm serious.

95
00:05:11,256 --> 00:05:12,855
You should have been free.

96
00:05:19,776 --> 00:05:20,855
It's settled then.

97
00:05:28,296 --> 00:05:28,895
Master!

98
00:05:29,376 --> 00:05:30,575
I beg you to save Chen!

99
00:05:30,896 --> 00:05:32,655
He's your own son, Master!

100
00:05:32,856 --> 00:05:34,255
Save him, Master!

101
00:05:34,416 --> 00:05:35,175
Enough!

102
00:05:36,576 --> 00:05:37,255
Do you think

103
00:05:37,456 --> 00:05:38,655
I haven't tried my best?

104
00:05:38,776 --> 00:05:40,735
He's your son, but also mine.

105
00:05:41,216 --> 00:05:43,695
Then save him, Master!

106
00:05:46,336 --> 00:05:47,375
It's only because

107
00:05:48,416 --> 00:05:50,495
he offended the Marshal's men.

108
00:05:57,896 --> 00:05:58,895
Defendant Zhou Yichen

109
00:05:59,336 --> 00:06:00,775
is guilty of murdering dockworkers,

110
00:06:01,216 --> 00:06:02,535
kidnapping women, and other felonies.

111
00:06:03,216 --> 00:06:04,095
Colluding with foreign merchants,

112
00:06:04,216 --> 00:06:05,095
bribing officials,

113
00:06:05,296 --> 00:06:06,495
and long-term opium smuggling

114
00:06:06,496 --> 00:06:08,295
are great evils harming the nation and its people.

115
00:06:08,616 --> 00:06:09,575
Given the severity,

116
00:06:09,576 --> 00:06:10,695
this court hereby sentences

117
00:06:10,816 --> 00:06:11,855
death by execution.

118
00:06:20,736 --> 00:06:21,575
It's snowing.

119
00:06:23,016 --> 00:06:24,575
Sister has come to see us.

120
00:07:54,816 --> 00:07:55,775
The morning is chilly.

121
00:07:56,336 --> 00:07:57,895
Your mother asked me to bring this.

122
00:08:06,456 --> 00:08:07,935
You came to mock me, didn't you?

123
00:08:12,176 --> 00:08:13,455
I came to ask you:

124
00:08:14,056 --> 00:08:14,975
three years ago,

125
00:08:16,096 --> 00:08:17,935
what exactly did you do to my sister?

126
00:08:19,056 --> 00:08:20,015
Who is your sister?

127
00:08:25,336 --> 00:08:26,015
Second Young Master,

128
00:08:27,296 --> 00:08:28,655
can't you see?

129
00:08:39,336 --> 00:08:40,655
You're Chuxue's sister.

130
00:08:46,296 --> 00:08:47,015
So...

131
00:08:48,456 --> 00:08:49,815
You came just to ask me

132
00:08:51,576 --> 00:08:52,375
whether

133
00:08:52,976 --> 00:08:54,175
I killed her back then.

134
00:08:54,976 --> 00:08:55,695
I admit

135
00:08:56,336 --> 00:08:57,415
I did suspect you.

136
00:08:58,336 --> 00:08:59,615
I never harmed her.

137
00:09:01,616 --> 00:09:03,095
She was my only family.

138
00:09:06,296 --> 00:09:07,135
Perhaps I...

139
00:09:08,416 --> 00:09:09,135
am just an

140
00:09:09,136 --> 00:09:10,895
utterly wicked villain.

141
00:09:12,856 --> 00:09:14,295
But my feelings for your sister

142
00:09:16,016 --> 00:09:17,095
were genuine.

143
00:09:17,976 --> 00:09:19,535
Then why did you slash her face?

144
00:09:21,176 --> 00:09:22,815
I didn't slash her face.

145
00:09:24,736 --> 00:09:25,855
She slashed at her own face,

146
00:09:28,616 --> 00:09:32,455
again and again.

147
00:09:32,936 --> 00:09:33,975
So what really happened

148
00:09:35,656 --> 00:09:36,775
three years ago?

149
00:09:40,216 --> 00:09:41,055
On New Year's Eve,

150
00:09:42,456 --> 00:09:43,895
I saw her staggering out

151
00:09:44,216 --> 00:09:45,815
of Father's room.

152
00:09:46,056 --> 00:09:47,815
Suspected... Father assaulted her.

153
00:09:48,576 --> 00:09:49,215
After that,

154
00:09:49,576 --> 00:09:51,935
I witnessed Second concubine tormenting her.

155
00:09:52,456 --> 00:09:54,215
I was furious but didn't know what to do.

156
00:09:55,216 --> 00:09:56,495
I knew she suffered greatly

157
00:09:56,496 --> 00:09:57,695
under Second concubine.

158
00:09:58,576 --> 00:09:59,935
I simply couldn't bear it.

159
00:10:00,136 --> 00:10:01,055
So under cover of night,

160
00:10:01,816 --> 00:10:03,295
I brought her to my private residence.

161
00:10:07,216 --> 00:10:08,055
Open the door.

162
00:10:14,336 --> 00:10:15,455
Is anyone there?

163
00:10:28,136 --> 00:10:28,815
Sister Chuxue.

164
00:10:36,296 --> 00:10:37,335
Second Young Master.

165
00:10:38,456 --> 00:10:40,255
Where is this, Second Young Master?

166
00:10:42,696 --> 00:10:43,895
We'll live here from now on.

167
00:10:43,896 --> 00:10:44,655
Alright?

168
00:10:46,256 --> 00:10:46,975
Here,

169
00:10:48,336 --> 00:10:50,095
no one will ever harm you.

170
00:10:52,136 --> 00:10:54,015
You'll be like the sculptures here

171
00:10:55,216 --> 00:10:56,375
flawless,

172
00:10:58,256 --> 00:10:59,535
untouched by dust.

173
00:11:01,456 --> 00:11:02,335
Second Young Master,

174
00:11:02,976 --> 00:11:05,055
please let me go.

175
00:11:07,976 --> 00:11:08,655
My father

176
00:11:08,896 --> 00:11:10,375
and Second concubine hurt you so badly.

177
00:11:11,496 --> 00:11:12,615
And you still want to return?

178
00:11:12,736 --> 00:11:14,415
By keeping me locked up here, how are you

179
00:11:14,536 --> 00:11:16,175
any different from them?

180
00:11:17,936 --> 00:11:19,175
I...

181
00:11:20,976 --> 00:11:22,415
I'm not like them.

182
00:11:24,456 --> 00:11:25,375
You don't understand.

183
00:11:26,176 --> 00:11:27,175
I'll protect you.

184
00:11:27,856 --> 00:11:29,495
I won't let anyone hurt you.

185
00:11:36,536 --> 00:11:37,335
Second Young Master,

186
00:11:38,416 --> 00:11:39,575
I'm not your possession.

187
00:11:40,456 --> 00:11:42,095
My family is waiting for me outside.

188
00:11:42,256 --> 00:11:43,175
Let me go.

189
00:11:44,936 --> 00:11:46,815
Am I not your family?

190
00:11:48,576 --> 00:11:49,855
I just want someone

191
00:11:50,456 --> 00:11:51,695
who cares about me as family.

192
00:11:53,456 --> 00:11:54,135
DCU

193
00:11:55,976 --> 00:11:57,535
didn't you used to care for me most?

194
00:11:57,576 --> 00:11:58,255
Sister,

195
00:11:58,256 --> 00:11:59,335
don't come near me.

196
00:12:00,216 --> 00:12:00,935
Let me leave.

197
00:12:04,736 --> 00:12:05,215
Otherwise,

198
00:12:05,296 --> 00:12:06,615
I'll slash my face!

199
00:12:06,736 --> 00:12:07,215
Don't!

200
00:12:07,736 --> 00:12:08,215
Don't!

201
00:12:08,936 --> 00:12:09,935
You're so perfect.

202
00:12:10,336 --> 00:12:11,735
I don't want you harming yourself.

203
00:12:12,096 --> 00:12:12,775
Sister!

204
00:12:20,816 --> 00:12:21,815
Move!

205
00:12:24,376 --> 00:12:25,015
No!

206
00:12:25,856 --> 00:12:26,455
Sister!

207
00:12:27,096 --> 00:12:27,815
Stop!

208
00:12:28,096 --> 00:12:28,655
Sister!

209
00:12:29,456 --> 00:12:31,735
Let me go! Let me go!

210
00:12:31,736 --> 00:12:33,815
Fine, you can go.

211
00:12:33,816 --> 00:12:34,935
Go! Just go!

212
00:12:48,696 --> 00:12:49,615
That night,

213
00:12:50,976 --> 00:12:52,615
I only wanted to protect her!

214
00:12:53,696 --> 00:12:55,255
If you truly wanted to protect her,

215
00:12:57,576 --> 00:12:58,215
why didn't you

216
00:12:58,216 --> 00:13:00,095
extend a helping hand when

217
00:13:00,336 --> 00:13:02,495
Master Zhou and Second concubine were harming her?

218
00:13:02,616 --> 00:13:03,495
I couldn't.

219
00:13:06,096 --> 00:13:07,095
Dared not.

220
00:13:09,176 --> 00:13:10,815
I feared disappointing my parents.

221
00:13:12,256 --> 00:13:13,375
I feared...

222
00:13:15,056 --> 00:13:16,215
that my intervention

223
00:13:18,136 --> 00:13:19,335
would cause this flower

224
00:13:20,336 --> 00:13:21,735
to wither faster.

225
00:13:22,736 --> 00:13:23,535
Second Young Master,

226
00:13:24,016 --> 00:13:25,175
see what I brought for you.

227
00:13:25,696 --> 00:13:26,855
Where did you go tonight?

228
00:13:27,256 --> 00:13:28,175
I found

229
00:13:28,176 --> 00:13:29,695
that childhood braised shop of yours

230
00:13:29,696 --> 00:13:31,095
on Langguan Lane

231
00:13:31,096 --> 00:13:32,895
and picked up some of their snacks.

232
00:13:33,056 --> 00:13:33,895
Try them

233
00:13:34,376 --> 00:13:35,815
Don't let the Third Concubine find out.

234
00:13:36,056 --> 00:13:37,175
You actually remembered?

235
00:13:40,176 --> 00:13:41,055
Third Concubine!

236
00:13:42,176 --> 00:13:43,055
Hurry!

237
00:13:44,736 --> 00:13:47,095
Third Concubine.

238
00:13:47,176 --> 00:13:48,775
I'm grinding ink for the young master.

239
00:13:49,696 --> 00:13:51,495
Someone seems to be looking for you.

240
00:13:52,456 --> 00:13:53,095
Okay.

241
00:13:53,296 --> 00:13:54,135
I'll be right there.

242
00:13:57,496 --> 00:13:58,215
Remember to eat.

243
00:14:04,336 --> 00:14:05,735
Chen, have you been getting

244
00:14:05,736 --> 00:14:07,415
too close to Chuxue recently?

245
00:14:08,216 --> 00:14:09,335
Mother, what do you mean by that?

246
00:14:09,936 --> 00:14:10,855
She and I...

247
00:14:30,576 --> 00:14:31,775
A mere maid

248
00:14:32,256 --> 00:14:34,335
has you this infatuated?

249
00:14:35,256 --> 00:14:36,215
Look at me!

250
00:14:37,896 --> 00:14:38,975
Have you forgotten the suffering

251
00:14:38,976 --> 00:14:40,695
we endured?

252
00:14:41,496 --> 00:14:43,695
Am I not important to you?

253
00:14:45,096 --> 00:14:46,135
Answer me!

254
00:14:48,856 --> 00:14:49,655
No,

255
00:14:50,416 --> 00:14:51,135
Mother.

256
00:14:52,656 --> 00:14:53,335
Don't be like this.

257
00:14:54,096 --> 00:14:54,815
I haven't!

258
00:14:58,736 --> 00:14:59,895
I'm telling you,

259
00:15:00,216 --> 00:15:02,335
if anything happens to Chuxue,

260
00:15:03,056 --> 00:15:04,735
it'll be because you pushed me to it.

261
00:15:05,136 --> 00:15:06,575
I'm innocent in this.

262
00:15:14,896 --> 00:15:15,815
Do you understand?

263
00:15:30,016 --> 00:15:30,575
Mother

264
00:15:32,016 --> 00:15:32,855
I understand.

265
00:15:36,616 --> 00:15:37,655
Ever since I was little,

266
00:15:39,616 --> 00:15:40,695
whenever I liked something,

267
00:15:41,696 --> 00:15:42,575
or cared about someone,

268
00:15:44,536 --> 00:15:45,735
my father and mother would find out

269
00:15:45,736 --> 00:15:47,095
and destroy them.

270
00:15:50,576 --> 00:15:52,255
I despise this family.

271
00:16:02,416 --> 00:16:03,615
How many times have I told you

272
00:16:03,616 --> 00:16:04,975
to stop playing with wood?

273
00:16:05,576 --> 00:16:06,335
Don't you know

274
00:16:07,016 --> 00:16:07,735
that bitch's child

275
00:16:07,736 --> 00:16:09,055
is already attending school?

276
00:16:09,856 --> 00:16:11,455
If you don't study properly,

277
00:16:11,656 --> 00:16:14,175
we will be stuck in this shabby room

278
00:16:14,176 --> 00:16:16,015
being bullied for the rest of our lives!

279
00:16:16,376 --> 00:16:17,175
If you don't study hard,

280
00:16:17,176 --> 00:16:18,615
how can you make your father like you?

281
00:16:18,816 --> 00:16:20,295
Why did I give birth to such a useless son?

282
00:16:20,536 --> 00:16:22,055
Mother, I'm wrong.

283
00:16:22,056 --> 00:16:23,215
I'm wrong.

284
00:16:23,416 --> 00:16:25,575
I will study hard.

285
00:16:26,016 --> 00:16:26,895
I'm telling you,

286
00:16:27,296 --> 00:16:28,215
remember this well.

287
00:16:28,736 --> 00:16:29,775
If I ever see you playing

288
00:16:30,096 --> 00:16:31,495
with this thing again,

289
00:16:31,496 --> 00:16:32,455
I'll smash it again.

290
00:16:38,176 --> 00:16:40,495
I will study hard.

291
00:16:40,576 --> 00:16:42,655
I will study.

292
00:16:44,616 --> 00:16:45,815
Father, it's calculated.

293
00:16:46,496 --> 00:16:47,375
Seems Wanzhi

294
00:16:48,296 --> 00:16:49,335
has taught you well.

295
00:16:49,736 --> 00:16:50,655
Master, you flatter me.

296
00:16:50,736 --> 00:16:51,615
I'm just glad you're happy with it.

297
00:16:51,856 --> 00:16:52,735
With my concubine's

298
00:16:53,736 --> 00:16:55,095
substantial family background,

299
00:16:55,736 --> 00:16:57,415
don't blame me if I see you on the street

300
00:16:58,176 --> 00:16:59,175
and cannot acknowledge you.

301
00:16:59,696 --> 00:17:00,695
But I promise you,

302
00:17:01,376 --> 00:17:02,495
When Chen gets a bit older,

303
00:17:03,136 --> 00:17:04,975
I will bring you back to the Zhou Residence.

304
00:17:05,496 --> 00:17:06,095
Okay?

305
00:17:06,736 --> 00:17:07,575
Great!

306
00:17:07,856 --> 00:17:08,615
Awesome!

307
00:17:17,656 --> 00:17:18,615
Fatherless child!

308
00:17:18,616 --> 00:17:19,495
You're lying!

309
00:17:19,496 --> 00:17:20,175
I have a father!

310
00:17:20,176 --> 00:17:21,935
He promised to visit me today!

311
00:17:27,056 --> 00:17:28,175
Give it back!

312
00:17:36,776 --> 00:17:38,055
Later, tell your grandfather

313
00:17:38,056 --> 00:17:39,295
that your studies are improving.

314
00:17:40,416 --> 00:17:40,775
Got it?

315
00:17:40,776 --> 00:17:41,535
Okay.

316
00:17:42,536 --> 00:17:43,135
Let's go.

317
00:17:43,776 --> 00:17:44,655
Father!

318
00:17:46,296 --> 00:17:47,175
Kid!

319
00:17:48,296 --> 00:17:49,295
You've mistaken me for someone else.

320
00:17:49,536 --> 00:17:50,415
Get out of the way!

321
00:17:50,576 --> 00:17:52,135
Where did this filthy kid come from?

322
00:17:53,376 --> 00:17:55,695
Dad, I want that wooden doll too.

323
00:17:55,696 --> 00:17:57,375
Alright, I'll buy it for you.

324
00:17:57,376 --> 00:17:58,255
But remember,

325
00:17:58,256 --> 00:17:59,135
in front of Grandma,

326
00:17:59,136 --> 00:18:00,335
stick up for me more.

327
00:18:00,576 --> 00:18:01,335
No problem!

328
00:18:03,456 --> 00:18:04,695
How many times have I told you?

329
00:18:04,976 --> 00:18:07,055
Don't acknowledge your father on the street!

330
00:18:07,216 --> 00:18:08,855
Do you even want me to enter the Zhou Residence?

331
00:18:14,656 --> 00:18:15,575
Alright.

332
00:18:16,136 --> 00:18:16,935
It's ridiculous.

333
00:18:17,696 --> 00:18:18,455
My father

334
00:18:19,256 --> 00:18:20,255
only loves himself.

335
00:18:21,176 --> 00:18:21,775
And I

336
00:18:22,896 --> 00:18:24,695
am just a convenient tool to him.

337
00:18:26,336 --> 00:18:27,375
Since you've seen through it,

338
00:18:29,136 --> 00:18:30,455
why help him cover it up?

339
00:18:30,776 --> 00:18:32,255
You said some things

340
00:18:33,736 --> 00:18:35,335
that I don't quite understand.
